@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_oflbky(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = wp.sin(wp.sin(wp.exp(v2 + 0.72)))
    v0 = 0.48
    v1 = 0.78
    tmp = wp.cos(wp.sin(wp.cos(v2 + 0.91)))
    v1 = tmp
    v1 = wp.abs((v1 / (v2 + 0.76 / v2 + 0.67)))
    data[tid] = v0
